room_title: Escape room "Operation Blackstone" by Escape FLA in Tampa
room_description: The Blackstone group is an ultra-exclusive, secret section of the American Intelligence Agency (AIA). As one of only a handful of members, you answer directly to the Director of Intelligence. Breaking protocol, the Director has summoned you to a clandestine meeting at your facility in the middle east. As you arrive, you are met by several other members of Blackstone who were also called in for the meet. You suddenly realize that all active Blackstone agents are here. Something is wrong, very wrong...
